Product Hunt launch (goal: Top 5 of the day)
Post on r/InternetIsBeautiful, r/DataHoarder, r/PrivacyGuides
Submit to Hacker News
Reach out to tech bloggers (TechCrunch, The Verge)

Growth (Weeks 10-20):

Add "Local Drop" feature (triggers network effects)
Campus ambassador program (5 colleges, $50 credit for referrals)
Twitter/X campaign: "We sent a 50GB file in under a minute" with screen recording
Integrate share button: "Share via TunnelDrop" embeddable widget

Viral Mechanics:

Every transfer shows recipient: "Sent via TunnelDrop.io"
"Copy link" includes branded short URL
Social proof: "1M+ files transferred" counter on homepage

