Set up repo, choose tech stack
Build signaling server (WebSocket)
Deploy to staging (Cloudflare Workers)

Week 3-4: Core Transfer

Implement sender flow (file picker, code generation)
Implement receiver flow (code entry, file download)
WebRTC connection establishment

Week 5-6: Polish

QR code generation
Progress indicators
Error handling (connection failed, timeout)
Responsive design

Week 7-8: Testing & Launch Prep

Cross-browser testing (Chrome, Firefox, Safari, Edge)
Cross-device testing (iOS, Android, desktop)
Performance optimization (large files, slow connections)
Write documentation, ToS, Privacy Policy

Deliverable: Functional web app at tunneldrop.io

Phase 2: Network Effects (Weeks 9-16)
Week 9-10: Local Discovery

Implement "Nearby Devices" peer detection
Device name/avatar customization
Privacy toggle

Week 11-12: Virality Features

Branded share links
Transfer counter on homepage
Social media meta tags (og:image, etc.)

Week 13-14: Analytics & Optimization

Privacy-respecting analytics (Plausible or Simple Analytics)
A/B test homepage copy
Speed optimizations based on user data

Week 15-16: Mobile UX

PWA (Progressive Web App) for "Add to Home Screen"
Optimize touch interactions
Mobile-specific onboarding

Deliverable: Viral growth engine active

Phase 3: Platform Expansion (Weeks 17-24)
