Electron app for Windows/Mac/Linux
Native file system integration (drag-drop from desktop)
Background transfers

Week 21-24: Mobile Apps (Optional)

React Native or native Swift/Kotlin
Background transfer support
Push notifications on completion

Deliverable: Native apps in beta

